        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Alexander Lofgren Veterans in Parks (VIP) Act</strong></p> <p><strong></strong>This bill makes the America the Beautiful-National Parks and Federal Recreational Lands Pass available, without charge, to members of the Armed Forces, veterans, and Gold Star Families. The pass covers the entrance fee and standard amenity recreation fee for all federal recreational lands and waters.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
